<abstract><t>This document describes a TRILL based DCI solution using VTSD. VTSD (Virtual TRILL Service/Switch Domain) is specified in [draft-VTSD]. This draft describes the advantages provided by a TRILL based DCI solution over an existing MPLS L2VPN solution, advantages such as bandwidth scaling and providing multiple active pseudowires.</t></abstract>

